table.caption: Table 87 – XObject Operator
head: Operands
Operator
Description
rows: Paint the specified XObject. The operand name shall appear as a key in the XObject subdictionary of the current resource dictionary. The associated value is a stream whose Type entry, if present, is XObject. The effect of Do depends on the value of the XObject’s Subtype entry, which may be Image, Form, or PS.
